__SqlaTable__.sql:
-- Note: Unless you save your query, these tabs will NOT persist if you clear your cookies or change browsers.

SELECT h.beneficio,c.pais_residencia,c.genero,c.hijos,c.edad,c.estado_civil FROM fact_ventas AS H JOIN dim_cliente as c ON c.cliente_key = h.cliente_key group by c.pais_residencia

-- Note: Unless you save your query, these tabs will NOT persist if you clear your cookies or change browsers.

SELECT l.pais as pais,c.genero,c.hijos,c.edad,c.estado_civil,c.cliente_key,f.fecha
FROM dim_lugar as l JOIN fact_ventas as h on h.lugar_salida_key=l.lugar_key 
JOIN dim_cliente AS c on c.cliente_key=h.cliente_key  
JOIN dim_fecha as f on h.fecha_salida_key=f.fecha_key

-- Note: Unless you save your query, these tabs will NOT persist if you clear your cookies or change browsers.

SELECT V.tipo_vuelo,c.genero,c.hijos,c.edad,c.estado_civil from dim_vuelo as v JOIN fact_ventas as h on h.vuelo_key = v.vuelo_key JOIN dim_cliente AS c on c.cliente_key=h.cliente_key
